Play a series of fast, short random short notes and you too can speak with aliens! VELOCITY controls attack time. PITCH WHEEL lets you add inflections on longer syllables (just be careful what you say, you don't want to create an intergalactic incident).

Vibrato is being generated by Step Seq 1 with Smooth Output enabled. Change vibrato rate by adjusting the Step Seq Rate knob. You can also change the vibrato rate by changing the Tempo, because the sequencer's clock is based on the BPM setting. Doing this will not affect the timing of the Stereo Delay (FX3).
